      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Literature synthesis of prior pedicle screw FEA validation studies",
      "description": "This intermediate evidence node consolidates findings from multiple prior independent validation studies of pedicle screw FEA models under ASTM F1717 loading, including Polikeit et al. (2003), Goel et al. (2006), and the FDA CDRH internal benchmark series (2011–2015). The synthesis establishes the prior plausibility envelope for model form error and material parameter sensitivity, informing acceptance bound selection for the primary QoI comparison. The aggregated body of evidence spans more than a decade of independent replication and is considered highly informative for the current COU."
    }
